WEBVTT

00:05:30.018 --> 00:05:33.894
And it will fundamentally transform
our relationship with local travel.

00:05:35.658 --> 00:05:38.727
In the past century,
flight connected our planet,

00:05:38.751 --> 00:05:41.688
in the next, it will reconnect
our local communities,

00:05:41.712 --> 00:05:44.569
and I hope it will
reconnect us to each other.

00:05:44.593 --> 00:05:45.760
Thank you.

00:05:45.784 --> 00:05:52.757
(Applause)

00:05:53.096 --> 00:05:56.032
Chris Anderson: OK, so when
these things first roll out --

00:05:56.056 --> 00:05:59.944
right now, it's a single
person aircraft, right?